  4069                                  ;       Routine:        GetConsoleString
  4070                                  ;
  4071                                  ;       Description:    This routine accepts keyboard input into a buffer.
  4072                                  ;
  4073                                  ;       In:             DS:EDX  target buffer address
  4074                                  ;                       ECX     maximum number of characters to accept
  4075                                  ;                       BH      echo to terminal
  4076                                  ;                       BL      terminating character
