  5759                                  ;       Routine:        ConInitPCIContext
  5760                                  ;
  5761                                  ;       Description:    This routine initializes a PCI structure.
  5762                                  ;
  5763                                  ;       In:             DS:EBX  PCI structure address
  5764                                  ;
